      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"tapestry\" thing sounds nice but it feels fake. Like, if you look at nature, it's not all beautiful threads. It's brutal. It's all about survival and being efficient. If something doesn't serve a purpose or can't adapt, it just gets cut out. I honestly feel like I'm that part. Like the part that's just failed the test. Am I just a mistake?",
